<br>
There are several reasons why VI would want to limit who has access to particular items.  Now what does VI have against twinking? One thing is that it makes other equipment obsolete.  Another reason is that it skews the power/level relationships that they use to design non-raid zones. Any items that a twink character would be able to obtain are considered junk time nowadays.<br>
<br>
Many people would like to see a balance between droppable and no-drop loot where the item is passed on to a reasonable level character. By putting the level limits on this stuff, they made it so only the targetted level range could use it.  This was previously only possible to control by making the item no drop and difficult to get the twink to.  Now they can remove the nodrop restriction and still be able to control who can wear it.  <br>
<br>
This will benefit the non-uber, non-wealthy group of players.  They will have access to some pretty darn nice gear and not have to compete with the rich players who want to outfit whatever class they are twinking this week. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uhawkline.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hawkline</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/28/02 2:57:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10517.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> Recommended level > No drop, but they really should label it as such so you don't get surprised. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upatofnaud.showPublicProfile?language=EN>patofnaud</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/28/02 2:59:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10517.topic&index=8>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> Yuppers. <br>
